{"tid":1472390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（鴨記）身在藍營，心在黃地","createTime":"2019-08-14T14:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:02:41.000Z","uid":105651,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab1b0847d5b5a6f1b590b73ba84260f9151d8a9","tid":1472390,"uid":105651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"首po<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5diX5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5diX5F.jpg&h=0301d6e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/220824_8e061bb7dca560151e5da765c0937e6c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F220824_8e061bb7dca560151e5da765c0937e6c.jpeg&h=2092fc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一間有深藍既高層，有深黃員工既公司！<br />\n我地係萬藍叢中一點黃，希望話比大家知，我地唔會同流合污！<br />\n抱歉我們是政府搵錢的公司，抱歉我們的上司是藍，我地亦只可提供微不足道既一手資料比大家！<br />\n我地收工亦一樣會同大家一齊去發夢，亦歡迎大家接我地收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家咁努力維持機場安全！<br />\n香港人加油！<br />\n5大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n支持成立獨立調查委員會！"},{"pid":"571c7ed741c1461b089008824a4c0f829ba9d9fb","tid":1472390,"uid":105651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"df0617908984958d62aa33379af8eee444e21071","tid":1472390,"uid":105651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"7faceb0cd1826f63090762c143caae03cb7e5ed6","tid":1472390,"uid":290717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2144a71ee4de558611092510b31d4307f17a21ac","tid":1472390,"uid":105651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:30:24.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"78590d0f630095d